1
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:33,160
I've suppressed her condition.

2
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:34,890
Until we find the antidote,

3
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,759
this needle must not be moved.

4
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:38,660
Don't worry. I'll give the order.

5
00:01:39,039 --> 00:01:40,080
Was Miss Chuyun

6
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:43,050
bitten by a poisonous creature in the mountains?

7
00:01:51,039 --> 00:01:52,370
It doesn't look like it.

8
00:01:57,759 --> 00:01:58,560
Ji Bai.

9
00:01:59,320 --> 00:02:01,120
Help me with this first.

10
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,160
My nose has stopped working.

11
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:03,490
I can't smell anything.

12
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,640
I've been deeply poisoned.

13
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:07,500
Cure me, quick.

14
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:09,639
Brother Shen, are you...

15
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,160
Ignore him.

16
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:13,370
His old problem is acting up again.

17
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:17,120
By the way, I still have some things to discuss with him,

18
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,250
so please excuse us.

19
00:02:19,079 --> 00:02:19,720
Let's go.

20
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:22,240
Let's go.

21
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,960
This medicine is too bitter.

22
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,620
Good medicine tastes bitter.

23
00:02:37,079 --> 00:02:38,800
I think you did it on purpose.

24
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:58,880
What is this? It's quite tasty.

25
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:01,650
This is malt sugar. Haven't you had it before?

26
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:12,720
I feel like I've tasted something similar.

27
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:14,160
Probably when I was little.

28
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:15,890
Forget it. It's not important.

29
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,520
My poison is cleared.

30
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:18,840
I'll be leaving then.

31
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:25,240
Your Highness.

32
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:39,180
The three poisoned people all had contact with him.

33
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:41,920
Good luck saving people.

34
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:42,850
You can't leave.

35
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:46,840
This poison needs to be broken down gradually.

36
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,440
You must stay.

37
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:49,600
What?

38
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:50,840
And let me tell you.

39
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,880
If you are more than a hundred steps away from me,

40
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,720
you will surely die.

41
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:16,560
Brother Shen, you don't seem to like it here.

42
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:21,380
People here are so hypocritical.

43
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:24,040
Your father obviously lost the bet.

44
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:24,920
But instead,

45
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:25,920
of helping me,

46
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:27,520
they turned the tables on me.

47
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:29,520
We are all neighbors here.

48
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:31,680
We have to show some respect.

49
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:32,600
Besides,

50
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:35,040
I have so many patients coming to my clinic.

51
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:38,400
Hypocrites.

52
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:43,120
Indeed.

53
00:04:58,840 --> 00:04:59,960
Thank you, Doctor.

54
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:00,520
Over there.

55
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:01,120
Okay.

56
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:23,040
Please leave if you are not a patient.

57
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:28,260
You must be Young Divine Physician Ji, disciple of the Gushan Divine Physician.

58
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,920
Years ago,

59
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:33,040
the Gushan Divine Physician traveled here with his disciple

60
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:35,500
and treated a mother and son from out of town.

61
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:37,800
I'm a family member of that mother and son.

62
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:39,200
I just wanted to ask you, Young Divine Physician,

63
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:41,720
if you still know their whereabouts.

64
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:50,120
I never treated that mother and son you mentioned.

65
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:52,760
My mentor has many disciples.

66
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,360
I only received a little guidance from him.

67
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:57,640
I'm not the disciple you're talking about.

68
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:59,040
Sorry to disappoint you.

69
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:04,380
Sorry to disturb you, Young Miracle Doctor.

70
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,720
I really don't understand.

71
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:55,320
Why do you insist on helping that old geezer see patients?

72
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:57,450
You haven't even fully recovered yet.

73
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:02,880
We can't just eat and stay here for free.

74
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:05,600
You are the Miracle Doctor's disciple.

75
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:06,640
You're doing him a favor.

76
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:08,370
You're bringing him business.

77
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:11,360
Shouldn't he treat us well?

78
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:19,920
You two.

79
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,720
Thank you for your hard work.

80
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:26,640
Miss Ji is the disciple of the Gushan Divine Physician.

81
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:28,760
Having you see patients in my humble shop

82
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:31,240
is truly an honor for us.

83
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:34,080
You flatter me, Mr. Du.

84
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:37,680
I was just lucky to receive some pointers from the Divine Physician.

85
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,680
I was desperate to save a life today,

86
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,760
so I may have exaggerated in front of your father.

87
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:43,720
Please forgive me, Mr. Du.

88
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,920
There is no need to be modest, Miss Ji.

89
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,250
We are closed for today.

90
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,740
Let me take you two to rest.

91
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:52,040
Don't you still have to organize the ledgers?

92
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:55,000
We know the way to our rooms, so we'll go back ourselves.

93
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,280
Very well. Farewell.

94
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:16,700
Give me some pointers.

95
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:20,480
Aren't you the Divine Physician's personal disciple?

96
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,280
You lied to me?

97
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:24,560
Yes, I lied.

98
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:39,520
That kid's surname is Shen.

99
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,120
A coincidence?

100
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:53,960
But he happens to be accompanied by a woman skilled in medicine.

101
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:57,890
What exactly is her relationship with the Divine Physician of Gushan?

102
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:16,320
Never mind. I'll investigate further before telling My Lord.

103
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:22,760
Ji Bai.

104
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:27,320
You doctors travel around and are well-informed.

105
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,920
Have you heard of Bao Dating?

106
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,600
Bao Dating?

107
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,640
Yes.

108
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:34,300
I read about it in a storybook.

109
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:37,480
Some people call them Jianghu Know-It-Alls.

110
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:39,080
Don't you know

111
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,520
that storybooks are fake?

112
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:42,160
If you want information,

113
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:44,640
there are old folks gathered at the street corner.

114
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:45,400
Go ask them.

115
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:46,520
You can't go wrong.

116
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:47,760
Really?

117
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:51,840
Try it and see.

118
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,280
Okay.

119
00:09:57,880 --> 00:09:59,840
I wonder if his foolishness

120
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:02,560
is feigned or real.

121
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:04,400
Doctor Ji.

122
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:06,680
Master Du.

123
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:10,720
What a pity.

124
00:10:11,920 --> 00:10:13,080
That girl Ji Bai

125
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:16,520
only received some casual pointers from the Divine Doctor of Gushan.

126
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:19,120
She probably doesn't even know where he lives.

127
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:23,440
I thought I could find the Young Master this time.

128
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:28,680
It makes sense.

129
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:31,120
Ji Bai is the Prime Minister's daughter.

130
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:34,560
I heard she married the Heir of the King of Northern Zhen recently.

131
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:37,120
How would the Prime Minister let his daughter

132
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:39,450
show her face in public to study medicine?

133
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:44,730
You are still inquiring about news from the Capital.

134
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:46,680
No need to be anxious, Elder Zhou.

135
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:47,880
I know what I'm doing.

136
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:49,080
Have some tea.

137
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,560
Master Du.

138
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:59,160
Where did this insect come from?

139
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:01,560
I extracted it from a patient

140
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:02,760
I treated today.

141
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:05,600
He was bitten while gathering things on the mountain.

142
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,680
You must be careful.

143
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:08,540
This insect is highly poisonous.

144
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:13,200
Do you recognize this, Miss Ji?

145
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:15,280
It is called Shixin.

146
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,080
If bitten,

147
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,810
it will lie dormant in the body.

148
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,040
Once triggered,

149
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:23,320
the victim will suffer excruciating heart pain.

150
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:27,010
I should go back to my room and rest.

151
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:30,520
Here is some medicine to kill it.

152
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:33,720
Be careful. Do not play with it.

153
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,440
Okay.

154
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:20,880
Doctor Ji, are you asleep?

155
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:23,200
I'm asleep. We'll talk tomorrow.

156
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,120
But I clearly heard your voice

157
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:27,040
coming from the desk.

158
00:12:27,160 --> 00:12:27,840
Open the door.

159
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,100
I just have a few words.

160
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,080
What are you doing?

161
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,320
I just wanted to ask,

162
00:12:42,520 --> 00:12:45,280
if I really can't be more than a hundred steps away from you.

163
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:46,080
Doesn't that mean

164
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:48,610
I have to sleep in the same room as you tonight?

165
00:13:20,880 --> 00:13:21,480
Yi Yinan.

166
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,640
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

167
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,040
Xiao Xiaoxue, Yi Yinan.

168
00:13:22,040 --> 00:13:23,240
Xiao Xiaoxue, Yi Yinan.

169
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:24,040
Xiao Xiaoxue.

170
00:13:50,040 --> 00:13:51,440
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

171
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:56,960
Lyu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.

172
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:56,960
Pan Xiulong.

173
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:57,200
Lyu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.

174
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:57,200
Pan.
